  "root_text": {
    "kp6:0.1": "Khuddakapāṭha 6 ",
    "kp6:0.2": "Ratanasutta ",
    "kp6:1.1": "Yānīdha bhūtāni samāgatāni, ",
    "kp6:1.2": "Bhummāni vā yāni va antalikkhe; ",
    "kp6:1.3": "Sabbeva bhūtā sumanā bhavantu, ",
    "kp6:1.4": "Athopi sakkacca suṇantu bhāsitaṁ. ",
    "kp6:2.1": "Tasmā hi bhūtā nisāmetha sabbe, ",
    "kp6:2.2": "Mettaṁ karotha mānusiyā pajāya; ",
    "kp6:2.3": "Divā ca ratto ca haranti ye baliṁ, ",
    "kp6:2.4": "Tasmā hi ne rakkhatha appamattā. ",
    "kp6:3.1": "Yaṁ kiñci vittaṁ idha vā huraṁ vā, ",
    "kp6:3.2": "Saggesu vā yaṁ ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ; ",
    "kp6:3.3": "Na no samaṁ atthi tathāgatena, ",
    "kp6:3.4": "Idampi buddhe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ; ",
    "kp6:3.5": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:4.1": "Khayaṁ virāgaṁ amataṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:4.2": "Yadajjhagā sakyamunī samāhito; ",
    "kp6:4.3": "Na tena dhammena samatthi kiñci, ",
    "kp6:4.4": "Idampi dhamme ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ; ",
    "kp6:4.5": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:5.1": "Yaṁ buddhaseṭṭho parivaṇṇayī suciṁ, ",
    "kp6:5.2": "Samādhimānantarikaññamāhu; ",
    "kp6:5.3": "Samādhinā tena samo na vijjati, ",
    "kp6:5.4": "Idampi dhamme ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ; ",
    "kp6:5.5": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:6.1": "Ye puggalā aṭṭha sataṁ pasatthā, ",
    "kp6:6.2": "Cattāri etāni yugāni honti; ",
    "kp6:6.3": "Te dakkhiṇeyyā sugatassa sāvakā, ",
    "kp6:6.4": "Etesu dinnāni mahapphalāni; ",
    "kp6:6.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:6.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:7.1": "Ye suppayuttā manasā daḷhena, ",
    "kp6:7.2": "Nikkāmino gotamasāsanamhi; ",
    "kp6:7.3": "Te pattipattā amataṁ vigayha, ",
    "kp6:7.4": "Laddhā mudhā nibbutiṁ bhuñjamānā; ",
    "kp6:7.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:7.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:8.1": "Yathindakhīlo pathavissito siyā, ",
    "kp6:8.2": "Catubbhi vātehi asampakampiyo; ",
    "kp6:8.3": "Tathūpamaṁ sappurisaṁ vadāmi, ",
    "kp6:8.4": "Yo ariyasaccāni avecca passati; ",
    "kp6:8.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:8.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:9.1": "Ye ariyasaccāni vibhāvayanti, ",
    "kp6:9.2": "Gambhīrapaññena sudesitāni; ",
    "kp6:9.3": "Kiñcāpi te honti bhusaṁ pamattā, ",
    "kp6:9.4": "Na te bhavaṁ aṭṭhamamādiyanti; ",
    "kp6:9.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:9.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:10.1": "Sahāvassa dassanasampadāya, ",
    "kp6:10.2": "Tayassu dhammā jahitā bhavanti; ",
    "kp6:10.3": "Sakkāyadiṭṭhī vicikicchitañca, ",
    "kp6:10.4": "Sīlabbataṁ vāpi yadatthi kiñci. ",
    "kp6:11.1": "Catūhapāyehi ca vippamutto, ",
    "kp6:11.2": "Chaccābhiṭhānāni abhabba kātuṁ; ",
    "kp6:11.3": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:11.4": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:12.1": "Kiñcāpi so kamma karoti pāpakaṁ, ",
    "kp6:12.2": "Kāyena vācā uda cetasā vā; ",
    "kp6:12.3": "Abhabba so tassa paṭicchadāya, ",
    "kp6:12.4": "Abhabbatā diṭṭhapadassa vuttā; ",
    "kp6:12.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:12.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:13.1": "Vanappagumbe yatha phussitagge, ",
    "kp6:13.2": "Gimhānamāse paṭhamasmiṁ gimhe; ",
    "kp6:13.3": "Tathūpamaṁ dhammavaraṁ adesayi, ",
    "kp6:13.4": "Nibbānagāmiṁ paramaṁ hitāya; ",
    "kp6:13.5": "Idampi buddhe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:13.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:14.1": "Varo varaññū varado varāharo, ",
    "kp6:14.2": "Anuttaro dhammavaraṁ adesayi; ",
    "kp6:14.3": "Idampi buddhe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:14.4": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:15.1": "Khīṇaṁ purāṇaṁ nava natthi sambhavaṁ, ",
    "kp6:15.2": "Virattacittāyatike bhavasmiṁ; ",
    "kp6:15.3": "Te khīṇabījā avirūḷhichandā, ",
    "kp6:15.4": "Nibbanti dhīrā yathāyaṁ padīpo; ",
    "kp6:15.5": "Idampi saṅghe ratanaṁ paṇītaṁ, ",
    "kp6:15.6": "Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:16.1": "Yānīdha bhūtāni samāgatāni, ",
    "kp6:16.2": "Bhummāni vā yāni va antalikkhe; ",
    "kp6:16.3": "Tathāgataṁ devamanussapūjitaṁ, ",
    "kp6:16.4": "Buddhaṁ namassāma suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:17.1": "Yānīdha bhūtāni samāgatāni, ",
    "kp6:17.2": "Bhummāni vā yāni va antalikkhe; ",
    "kp6:17.3": "Tathāgataṁ devamanussapūjitaṁ, ",
    "kp6:17.4": "Dhammaṁ namassāma suvatthi hotu. ",
    "kp6:18.1": "Yānīdha bhūtāni samāgatāni, ",
    "kp6:18.2": "Bhummāni vā yāni va antalikkhe; ",
    "kp6:18.3": "Tathāgataṁ devamanussapūjitaṁ, ",
    "kp6:18.4": "Saṅghaṁ namassāma suvatthi hotūti. ",
    "kp6:19.1": "Ratanasuttaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "kp6:0.1": "Basic Passages 6 ",
    "kp6:0.2": "Gems ",
    "kp6:1.1": "Whatever beings have gathered here, ",
    "kp6:1.2": "on the ground or in the sky, ",
    "kp6:1.3": "may beings all be of happy heart, ",
    "kp6:1.4": "and listen carefully to what is said. ",
    "kp6:2.1": "So pay heed, all you beings, ",
    "kp6:2.2": "have love for humankind, ",
    "kp6:2.3": "who day and night bring offerings; ",
    "kp6:2.4": "please protect them diligently. ",
    "kp6:3.1": "There’s no wealth this life or the next, ",
    "kp6:3.2": "no sublime gem in the heavens, ",
    "kp6:3.3": "that equals the Realized One. ",
    "kp6:3.4": "This sublime gem is in the Buddha: ",
    "kp6:3.5": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:4.1": "Ending, dispassion, the undying, the sublime, ",
    "kp6:4.2": "attained by the Sakyan Sage immersed in samādhi; ",
    "kp6:4.3": "there is nothing equal to that Dhamma. ",
    "kp6:4.4": "This sublime gem is in the Dhamma: ",
    "kp6:4.5": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:5.1": "The purity praised by the highest Buddha, ",
    "kp6:5.2": "is said to be the “immersion with immediate fruit”; ",
    "kp6:5.3": "no equal to that immersion is found. ",
    "kp6:5.4": "This sublime gem is in the Dhamma: ",
    "kp6:5.5": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:6.1": "The eight individual persons praised by the good ",
    "kp6:6.2": "are the four pairs of the Holy One’s disciples; ",
    "kp6:6.3": "they are worthy of religious donations, ",
    "kp6:6.4": "what’s given to them is very fruitful. ",
    "kp6:6.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:6.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:7.1": "Dedicated to Gotama’s dispensation, ",
    "kp6:7.2": "strong-minded, free of sense desire, ",
    "kp6:7.3": "they’ve attained the goal, plunged into freedom from death, ",
    "kp6:7.4": "and enjoy the quenching they’ve freely gained. ",
    "kp6:7.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:7.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:8.1": "As Indra’s pillar rooted in earth ",
    "kp6:8.2": "is not shaken by the four winds, ",
    "kp6:8.3": "I say a true person is like this, ",
    "kp6:8.4": "who sees the noble truths in experience. ",
    "kp6:8.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:8.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:9.1": "Those who fathom the noble truths ",
    "kp6:9.2": "taught by the one of deep wisdom, ",
    "kp6:9.3": "do not take an eighth life, ",
    "kp6:9.4": "even if they are hugely negligent. ",
    "kp6:9.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:9.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:10.1": "When they attain to vision ",
    "kp6:10.2": "they give up three things: ",
    "kp6:10.3": "substantialist view, doubt, and any ",
    "kp6:10.4": "attachment to precepts and observances. ",
    "kp6:11.1": "They’re freed from the four places of loss, ",
    "kp6:11.2": "and cannot do six things. ",
    "kp6:11.3": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:11.4": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:12.1": "Even if they do a bad deed ",
    "kp6:12.2": "by body, speech, or mind, ",
    "kp6:12.3": "they are unable to conceal it; ",
    "kp6:12.4": "they say this inability applies to one who has seen the truth. ",
    "kp6:12.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:12.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:13.1": "Like a tall forest tree crowned with flowers ",
    "kp6:13.2": "in the first month of summer; ",
    "kp6:13.3": "that’s how he taught the superb Dhamma, ",
    "kp6:13.4": "leading to extinguishment, the ultimate benefit. ",
    "kp6:13.5": "This sublime gem is in the Buddha: ",
    "kp6:13.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:14.1": "The superb, knower of the superb, giver of the superb, bringer of the superb; ",
    "kp6:14.2": "taught the superb Dhamma supreme. ",
    "kp6:14.3": "This sublime gem is in the Buddha: ",
    "kp6:14.4": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:15.1": "The old is ended, nothing new is produced. ",
    "kp6:15.2": "their minds have no desire for future rebirth. ",
    "kp6:15.3": "Withered are the seeds, there’s no desire for growth, ",
    "kp6:15.4": "those attentive ones are extinguished just like this lamp. ",
    "kp6:15.5": "This sublime gem is in the Saṅgha: ",
    "kp6:15.6": "by this truth, may you be well! ",
    "kp6:16.1": "Whatever beings have gathered here, ",
    "kp6:16.2": "on the ground or in the sky: ",
    "kp6:16.3": "the Realized One is honored by gods and humans! ",
    "kp6:16.4": "We bow to the Buddha! May you be safe! ",
    "kp6:17.1": "Whatever beings have gathered here, ",
    "kp6:17.2": "on the ground or in the sky: ",
    "kp6:17.3": "the Realized One is honored by gods and humans! ",
    "kp6:17.4": "We bow to the Dhamma! May you be safe! ",
    "kp6:18.1": "Whatever beings have gathered here, ",
    "kp6:18.2": "on the ground or in the sky: ",
    "kp6:18.3": "the Realized One is honored by gods and humans! ",
    "kp6:18.4": "We bow to the Saṅgha! May you be safe! "
  },
